##########################
 COMMAND
      man topic
 DESCRIPTION
      Prints information requested by 'topic'.
	  Allow to get more information about specific message (ADV-...)
	     or command.
 ARGUMENTS
      topic - one or more SDC files to be read
              Can be one of 'ADV-...' or command.
			  Warning printed if no topic found.
			  Example:
			     man ADV-1              prints details of message
				 man read_sdc           prints 'read_sdc' description
